Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.28,0:00:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缪雪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缪雪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.73,0:00:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在抱歉  我们已经尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么美丽的面庞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是它已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无法再动弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩特菈卡也意外的有些很温柔的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缪雪儿比我想的还有精神  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.41,0:01:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像跳过了一话一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的场先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚来到这里就被卷进了这么要命的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.03,0:01:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那些恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来幕后黑手是帝国的反皇帝派贵族们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.96,0:01:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侵略者吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没睡好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是侵略者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加纳君  我们的工作是保护日本的国家利益
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是上课的第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧张也是没办法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事物的定义会因为看法的不同而不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果认为自己是侵略者的话  那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果认为不是  就不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太钻牛角尖比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要轻松地去考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何让宅文化在这个国家里流行起来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  一股土气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然和矮人在一个屋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是受不了这股味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:03:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此  他们的本职就是挖土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以说这一存在自身就是有着一股土气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们才是只会削木头的森林猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始上课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肃静  肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落座
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是本校校长加纳慎一的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅是他  我也担任教师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请记住这点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么校长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么开始上课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:56.15,SPEC7,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}一个月后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  缪雪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  这一个月没有好好打扫过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会  请不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是缪雪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷  学校怎么样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想象的还要顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了记住新的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的热情十分高涨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我的课都会认真听
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为老爷很会教人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会教人  我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是没有学习过的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也因为老爷而学会了怎么读文字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的十分感谢老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缪雪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始  我们终于将要开始宅文化的课程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先我将教你们一些基础单词
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  请大家跟着我念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.94,SPEC7,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(202,293,214,293)}10岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很像样了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  第一课
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对领域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对领域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一上来就这么高难度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:32.42,SPEC7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(108,70)}10岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  罗米尔达君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对…  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对领域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝  绝对领域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是指超短裙和过膝袜之间的这个部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:44.10,SPEC7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(108,70)}10岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是指大腿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用更加大局观的视点来看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超短裙  大腿  过膝袜交织而成的黄金比率
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由此而诞生的究极的走光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:57.11,SPEC7,,0,0,0,,{\move(200,293,228,293)}10岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,18岁以下穿着超短裙和过膝袜这点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该由法律强行规定为义务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  来看下一个单词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二课
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没穿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没穿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没穿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没穿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  洛伊克君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没穿是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没穿!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  正确的应该是故意让你脑补成没有穿的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到  到底是哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题不在于是否真的穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是由想象力编织而成的至高的走光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  第三课
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎一  停下停下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你教的东西太偏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校长的教学太难了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始  我来教大家一些更基础的单词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实有点太过干劲十足了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过美埜里小姐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会教一些一般人所知道的专门用语吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  第一课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是受  总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是表达备受周围人宠爱的状态的词
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  这个词仅仅适用于男性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然攻的一方也全是男性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  是喜欢男人的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请称之为BL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BL？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Boys Love的略称
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了哦  BL是指
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,描写男人之间时而甘甜时而激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充满着浪漫气息的文学作品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是这个作品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美埜里小姐  停下  停下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生还未成年  请不要拿出这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  第二课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男孩纸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs16}伪娘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男孩纸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  罗米尔达同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和我们之前学的男孩子不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声调要更利落一点  男孩纸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男…男孩纸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指的是看起来是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是身体是男孩子的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在BL里  男孩纸是令人欲罢不能的要素之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美埜里小姐  果然是那方面的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不能只顾着一味地教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个世界的价值观和日本不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉这样下去只是强行灌输而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美埜里小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宅邸旁边出现了没见过的人影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人影？  不是布鲁克吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经注册过了  不会引发侵入者警报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁克不会潜伏在草丛里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美埜里小姐  美埜里小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好等待救援吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  对方好像只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兽娘出现啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…  怎么了  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你点话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾儿比娅·哈娜伊蔓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你问我是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  如你所见是个流浪画家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  这画得和职业的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会画画不一定是画家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是巴哈拉姆的间谍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间谍？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  巴哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈拉姆王国
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是艾尔丹特帝国的邻国
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔丹特帝国和巴哈拉姆是敌对关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双方当然也会互送间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经不是第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们的身边  会定期发现有间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想象的还要快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊  要把我带去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明监视着我们的不止有间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会被怎么处置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛  如果间谍被抓住会被拷问然后处刑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她  估计自己都不知道自己在进行间谍活动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆在巴哈拉姆的立场上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是被当做了大量投放的消耗品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在画画就要被处刑什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:23.94,SPEC5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(115,207)\be1}艾儿比娅·哈娜伊蔓
